{"tid":602770,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"低收入人士：學生、家庭主婦亦有$4000","createTime":"2018-03-23T07:58:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-23T08:10:18.000Z","uid":178036,"like":2,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"4a10b264215e1539e08c392277a213451d113d4f","tid":602770,"uid":178036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"獲發4000港元津貼的合資格條件如下：<br />\n<br />\n-今年12月31日前年滿18歲或以上<br />\n<br />\n-通常居港<br />\n<br />\n-無物業<br />\n<br />\n-退稅少於$4000<br />\n<br />\n-無交薪俸稅<br />\n<br />\n-無領綜援、生果金、長津、殘津或低津<br />\n<br />\n-持物業但無需交稅、差餉寬免若不足$4000可補差額<br />\n<br />\n-財政預算案中獲「三糧」的社會保障人士，若不足$4000可補差額<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">如果仲係學生但有翻part time仲有無錢收？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span>"},{"pid":"7831cc4df4ef84d04c8f784ac0b30926a232d275","tid":602770,"uid":2419,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:06:32.000Z","msg":"弱智咪撚上網啦"},{"pid":"89b1603870df758d240f6ad753d99feae52883b7","tid":602770,"uid":21306,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-23T08:10:18.000Z","msg":"文盲？"}]}